Interface ExtensionInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

      • namespaceToJavaPackagePrefix

        java.lang.String namespaceToJavaPackagePrefix(java.net.URI ns)
        Return the java package prefix for the given namespace. This prefix is prepended to the names of published classes to obtain a unique Java name. For the localNamespace or platformNamespace, returns the empty string.
        Returns:
        the java package prefix string

        The list of directories and codebases to search.
